&lt;p data-start=&quot;80&quot; data-end=&quot;301&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Kia Santa Monica is seeking an experienced Automotive F&amp;amp;I Sales Consultant to join our team! We are looking for a motivated, results-driven professional who is ready to hit the ground running and make an immediate impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
