&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Monitors processed deals for funding and follows up and/or correct deals which are incomplete or the lender is unable to fund.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Provide customers a thorough explanation of structure of deal, aftermarket products and all warranty products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
